    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款小制作游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>Rosttle是一款个人开发的2D俯视角射击游戏。游戏中，玩家每一局需要尽可能的存活，吃到场上的黄色精力点，避开地图障碍物，玩家需要用尽各种手段消灭怪物，获得金币，获得奖励。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每把武器都有特殊的被动，不同枪械组合出不同流派</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏战斗，游戏难度逐渐递增</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏为个人开发，游戏未来将会开启长期更新支持</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器被动组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中物品的被动将会相互影响，根据背包中物品的特性，对物品的位置做出适当的调整，将会得到&quot;一加一大于二&quot;的效果，你的角色也会更加强大</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机生成的游戏地图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将会进入到不同的房间，不管你选择哪一条路径，每条路径上你会遭遇不同的事件，但最终目的都是通往最高处</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每局回合奖励</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在结束一场战斗后，根据武器的特性，以及背包已有的武器特性，选择一把武器添加到背包中，增加角色的强度和游戏难度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机事件</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，你将会遭遇不同的随机事件，迫使你做出选择，而你的每次选择将会影响到你的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
